{
  "id": "class_0060",
  "name": "Windborne Herald of the Fractured Court",
  "title_completion": "a Windborne Herald of the Fractured Court",
  "flavor_text": "You did not ask to carry the Mad King's proclamations across the howling throne room, yet the parchments found your hands all the same. Your voice, blessed by some forgotten wind-saint, can silence a lord mid-sentence or lift a decree so high it becomes law before it lands. The court does not love you \u2014 but it obeys, and in this kingdom, that is holier than love.",
